{"slug":"sirkuler-10-218-5020","reference":"Sirkuler_10_218","gazette":"Seminer Duyurusu (25 Aralık 2010)","title":"-","date":"01 Ocak 2010","bodyHtml":"<p>\n\t<font face=\"Times New Roman\" size=\"3\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\" size=\"3\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\" size=\"3\">SEMİNER DUYURUSU</font></font></font></p>\n<p>\n\t<font face=\"Times New Roman\" size=\"3\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\" size=\"3\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\" size=\"3\">&nbsp;</font><br />\n\t<font face=\"Times New Roman\" size=\"3\">25 Aralık Cumartesi g&uuml;n&uuml; UPS Haluk &Uuml;ndeğer Konferans Salonu&#39;nda G&Uuml;MR&Uuml;K M&Uuml;STEŞARLIĞI ve DIŞ TİCARET M&Uuml;STEŞARLIĞI yetkililerinin katılımıyla &ldquo;Dahilde İşleme Rejimi&rdquo; konusu ele alınacaktır. </font></font></font></p>\n<p>\n\t<font face=\"Times New Roman\" size=\"3\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\" size=\"3\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\" size=\"3\">Siz değerli m&uuml;şterilerimizin katılımını arz ederiz.</font></font></font></p>\n<p>\n\t<font face=\"Times New Roman\" size=\"3\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\" size=\"3\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\" size=\"3\">Saygılarımızla,</font></font></font></p>\n<p>\n\t<font face=\"Times New Roman\" size=\"3\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\" size=\"3\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\" size=\"3\">&nbsp;</font></font></font></p>\n<p>\n\t<font face=\"Times New Roman\" size=\"3\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\" size=\"3\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\" size=\"3\">GİB G&Uuml;MR&Uuml;K M&Uuml;ŞAVİRLİĞİ </font></font></font></p>\n\n                                <a target=\"_blank\" class=\"text-danger\" href=\"https://portal.ugm.com.tr/shared/DosyaAl.ashx?refno=REFSirkuler_10_218.zip&amp;arsivid=4470e5e5-2f58-4742-ac7f-bb0f363fc560\">\n                                    https://portal.ugm.com.tr/shared/DosyaAl.ashx?refno=REFSirkuler_10_218.zip&amp;arsivid=4470e5e5-2f58-4742-ac7f-bb0f363fc560\n                                </a>"}
